tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE electric_vehicles (
    vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand VARCHAR(255),
    model VARCHAR(255),
    year INT,
    battery_capacity INT
);

CREATE TABLE charging_sessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    station_id INT,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE ChargingEvents (
    event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    station_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    energy_delivered DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE electric_vehicles (
  vehicle_id INT,
  brand VARCHAR,
  model VARCHAR,
  battery_capacity DECIMAL,
  energy_consumption DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE charging_sessions (
  session_id INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  station_id INT,
  vehicle_id INT,
  energy_delivered DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE vehicle_locations (
  location_id INT,
  vehicle_id INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  latitude DECIMAL,
  longitude DECIMAL
);
